msgid "Inserts a single widget into an existing Elementor post. KEY WIDGET SLUGS — Header: site-logo, navigation-menu, hfe-search-button, hfe-cart. Footer: copyright, retina (logo), social-icons. Pages: heading, text-editor, image, button, hfe-infocard, hfe-counter. Use list-widget-types to discover all available slugs."
msgstr "Insère un seul widget dans un post Elementor existant. SLUGS DE WIDGET CLÉS — En-tête : site-logo, navigation-menu, hfe-search-button, hfe-cart. Pied de page : copyright, retina (logo), social-icons. Pages : heading, text-editor, image, button, hfe-infocard, hfe-counter. Utilisez list-widget-types pour découvrir tous les slugs disponibles."

